1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,200
[agent] Thanks for joining. Can you describe the current onboarding flow end-to-end?

2
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:09,700
[customer] Users sign up, then we send them to three separate setup pages.

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:14,400
[agent] What’s the biggest point of confusion in those pages?

4
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:20,000
[customer] Permissions. People aren’t sure which role to pick, so they abandon.

5
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:24,600
[agent] Got it. We can simplify roles and delay advanced options until later.

